Name: GeographicStructureSchemeName
Description: A name for the GeographicStructureScheme. May be expressed in multiple languages. Repeat the element to express names with different content, for example different names for different systems.

Name: Label
Description: A display label for the GeographicStructureScheme. Supports multiple language versions of the same content as well as optional formatting of the content. Repeat for labels with different content, for example, labels with differing length limitations.

Name: Description
Description: A description of the GeographicStructureScheme. Supports multiple language versions of the same content as well as optional formatting of the content.

Name: GeographicStructureSchemeReference
Description: The inclusion of an existing GeographicStructureScheme in the parent scheme by reference.

Name: GeographicStructureReference
Description: Used to describe any level of geography, including overall coverage and each of the lower levels.

Name: GeographicStructureGroupReference
Description: In-line description of a group of GeographicStructure.
